#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Bonfire_00"
msgid ""
"Time Flies<1.ra>If you ever want to advance time, seek out a cozy "
"campfire.\n"
"There, you can pass the time until morning, noon, or night."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Bonfire_01"
msgid ""
"Making a Campfire<1.ra>To start a campfire, simply set some wood ablaze. "
"You can use\n"
"a torch or some flint to do just that."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Bonfire_02"
msgid ""
"Time Flies<1.ra>Monsters thrive at nighttimeâ€”as do other things that can "
"make\n"
"adventuring dangerous. If you're low on hearts at night, find a\n"
"campfire and lay low until morning."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Gimmick_00"
msgid ""
"Cold Water<1.ra>Swimming in cold water will lower your body heat and "
"cause you to\n"
"take damage. Cooked food and special garb won't help you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Gimmick_01"
msgid ""
"Hot Springs<1.ra>These lush, thermal baths are found throughout the "
"world.\n"
"You can relax in them for a while to replenish your hearts."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Gimmick_02"
msgid ""
"Pools of Malice<1.ra>Poisonous bogs formed by water that was sullied "
"during the\n"
"Great Calamity. Coming into contact with one will hurt you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Gimmick_03"
msgid ""
"Bottomless Bog<1.ra>A quagmire that will draw you in... Sink in too "
"deeply, and you'll be\n"
"unable to escape."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Gimmick_04"
msgid ""
"Rafts<1.ra>Rafts with sails can move when pushed by the wind. Or you can "
"get\n"
"them moving yourself if you have a Korok leaf."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: icon
msgctxt "Knowledge_00"
msgid ""
"Finding Your Way<1.ra>If you get lost, try climbing to higher ground and "
"looking around.\n"
"Press <2.ic> to pull out your scope so you can see even farther."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Knowledge_01"
msgid ""
"Ancient Furnaces<1.ra>These energy furnaces glow with a blue flame. They "
"are said to be\n"
"creations of the ancient Sheikah race. It may be true, as they've\n"
"been burning for 10,000 years."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Knowledge_02"
msgid ""
"Setting Fires<1.ra>Wooden objects and dry grass catch fire easily. Be "
"careful around\n"
"such things while holding a lit torch."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Knowledge_03"
msgid ""
"Burning Things<1.ra>Dry grass catches fire especially easily, and that "
"fire spreads quickly."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Knowledge_04"
msgid ""
"Updrafts<1.ra>When fire spreads, it creates an updraft. You can use the "
"paraglider\n"
"to catch that updraft and ride it high into the sky."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Knowledge_05"
msgid ""
"Granters of Boons <1.ra>At the far reaches of the continent, there is a "
"being\n"
"that trades in Heart Containers and Stamina Vessels."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Knowledge_06"
msgid ""
"Goddess Statues<1.ra>These ancient monuments depict the Goddess "
"worshipped in Hyrule\n"
"since time out of mind. You can trade four Spirit Orbs to one for \n"
"a Stamina Vessel or a Heart Container."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Temperature_00"
msgid ""
"Temperature Changes<1.ra>The temperature will change depending on your "
"location and the time\n"
"of day. It's a good idea to pay close attention to fluctuations in\n"
"temperature when you're out roaming."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Temperature_01"
msgid ""
"Beat the Heat<1.ra>The strong rays of the sun during a desert day will "
"inflict damage if\n"
"you're unprepared. You'll need to spend time in the shade or water\n"
"or equip special armor specially made for high temperatures."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Temperature_02"
msgid ""
"Surviving the Cold<1.ra>Even in frigid climates, the heat of a campfire "
"can keep you warm.\n"
"Holding a lit torch is another good way to stave off the cold."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Time_00"
msgid ""
"The Joys of Night<1.ra>Some animals and insects only come out when it's "
"dark. Keep an eye\n"
"out for them!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Time_01"
msgid ""
"Nighttime Monsters<1.ra>When night falls, skeletal Stal monsters will "
"emerge from the ground.\n"
"Stay vigilant!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Weather_00"
msgid ""
"Lightning Strikes<1.ra>Lightning has a tendency to strike anything "
"metallic. Whenever you\n"
"hear thunder, it's a good idea to remove any metallic equipment\n"
"before you get fried."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Weather_01"
msgid ""
"The Joys of Rain<1.ra>Some animals love playing in the rain, and there "
"are certain plants\n"
"that only bloom during rainstorms. Keep an eye out for them!"
msgstr ""

